    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Bar Service\nAPERITIFS\nSherry\nCampari\nVermouth, sweet or dry\nSPIRITS\nScotch, American and Canadian Whiskies\nGin • Rum • Vodka\nWINES\nSelected red or white wines\nChampagne is also available at\ncurrent bar tariff rate\nLIQUEURS\nCognac • Drambuie • Cointreau\nTia Maria • Port\nBEERS\nEnglish beers\nLager\nSOFT DRINKS\nSquashes: Orange • Lemon • Lime\nColas • Ginger Ale\nBitter Lemon • Tonic Water\nMineral Water\nCAN/USA-LHR MENU A\u0026B Econ QC 16986\nMenu\nFresh honeydew and cantaloup melon with\nstrawberry and a light lime\nGrilled fillet of Atlantic salmon with\nBay shrimps, spring onions and capers,\ndressed with lemon herb sauce and served\nwith leaf spinach, carrots and\nparsley potatoes\nor\nPrime fillet steak in a rich red wine sauce\nwith mushroom and bacon served with\nbuttered beans, cherry tomato\nand potato gnocchis\nTraditional bread and butter pudding\nglazed with apricot sauce\nCoffee or decaffeinated coffee\nWe apologise if, owing to previous passenger\nselection, your choice is not available\nRefreshments\nwill be served",
      "WINES \u0026 SPIRITS\nCONNOISSEUR\nCLA\nWUNITED"
